org.apache.beam.artifact.local

Class LocalArtifactStagingLocation

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.apache.beam.artifact.local.LocalArtifactStagingLocation

  • public class LocalArtifactStagingLocation
extends java.lang.Object
    A location where the results of an LocalFileSystemArtifactStagerService are stored and where the retrieval service retrieves them from.
